_:Nee26a02edcda4f9d9464cdf47582183d <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Matthew Pennycook was appointed Minister of State at the Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government on 6 July 2024. He was elected as the MP for Greenwich and Woolwich in May 2015.</p>\n" .
